node.text: The iconic former editor in chief of Teen Vogue, our newest instructor is an award-winning, bestselling, TV-hosting, trendsetting, dream-chasing, one-of-a-kind trailblazer. And she’s ready to teach you how to craft the future you want—even if you don’t know what it is yet. Introducing @elainewelteroth’s MasterClass on designing your career.
